verbose_text: Compared with the group without symptoms of PSC, the group with PSC (cases) showed significantly higher levels of AST (22.5 U/l vs. 70.0 U/l, p < 0.001), ALP (359.0 U/l vs. 602.0 U/l, p < 0.001), and IgG4 (56.0 vs. 73.0, p = 0.02).
